description: The main course is my favorite part of a three-course meal.
I like preparing/cooking my own meals.
Yellow is one of my favorite colors.
I like staying indoors and relaxing at home.
I play video games on a regular basis.
I don't mind overspending on new experiences.
I enjoy eating fruits and/or vegetables.
When making a bowl of cereal, I pour milk first, then cereal.
Grades are very important to me, and consider “B's” bad.
